data.title: Miettunen I Cabinet
data.text:
Martti Miettunen's first cabinet was the 46th government of Republic of Finland. Cabinet's time period was from August 14, 1961 to April 13, 1962. It was Minority government.

Assembly Minister Period of office Party Prime Minister

Martti Miettunen August 14, 1961- April 13, 1962 Agrarian League Minister of Foreign Affairs
